{
  "stem": "10446.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And these people, unbeknownst to us, had invited another couple, a man, Charles Adler, who happened to be president of Wallachs, the men's stores.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They are just about disappearing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Now the last store is on 45th Street and Fifth Avenue now.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that is disappearing, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "At that time, there were about eight stores all over New York City.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had no idea who he was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if he had told me, I wouldn't have known either.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he looked me over, and after dinner he said to me, would you like to work, to work for me?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm the president of Wallachs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, oh, really, not knowing what it was, but jobs were extremely hard to get in those days.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was the-- still the tail-end of the Depression.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was very difficult to get a job.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I was delighted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't expect that, and I said, certainly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he said, report on Monday morning to the manager of the store, Mr.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Mann ?] in the Empire State Building.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That store occupied the good part of the ground floor of the Empire State Building, facing Fifth Avenue.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it only disappeared a few years ago.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It's now a Duane Reade store.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I reported, and I became a stock boy with the DHP.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I had to see that the shirts were properly lined up in the showcases, the ties were hanging well from the racks, and when a sale was made, I had to go downstairs, have it wrapped, and then I handed it to the customer.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "How did you feel doing this sort of work?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Absolutely fine.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was happy to have work, to earn $18 a week, which was a good salary.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
